    "body": "Thanks! That seems to have solved the problem... \n\npandas 0.16.1\nmatplotlib 1.4.3\n\n``` python\ngs = mpl.gridspec.GridSpec(2, 4)\nax1 = plt.subplot(gs[0,:-1])\nax2 = plt.subplot(gs[0,-1])\nax3 = plt.subplot(gs[1,:-2])\nax4 = plt.subplot(gs[1,-2:])\n\ndf.A.plot(ax=ax1)\ndf.B.plot(ax=ax2)\ndf.C.plot(ax=ax3)\ndf.D.plot(ax=ax4)\n\ngs.tight_layout(plt.gcf())\n```\n\n![pandas3](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7450204/7682586/61a6a806-fd79-11e4-82db-be4cd4f80651.png)\n"
